spans.text: the View : Ever Gothic Forms were known in Greece , To spoil the well-proportioned Piece : And in our Verse ever Monkish Rhimes Had jangled their fantastic Chimes : Ever on the flowery Lands of Rhodes Those Knights had fixed their dull Abodes , Who knew not much to paint or write , Nor cared to pray , nor dared to fight : Protogenes , Historians note , Lived there , a Burgess Scot and Lot ; And , as old Pliny's Writings show , Apelles did the same at Co.
